", "username": "libsoftiktok"}, "content": "WOW. Senator Harry Reid, a DEMOCRAT, introduced a bill in 1993 to END birthright citizenship for illegal aliens.\n\nBut if Trump wants to do it, Democrats call it \"rAcIsT\"\n\n", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 58935}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZD2Pveg", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 146, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8536416, "raw_content": "1) Ending Alimony: Most men refuse to get married because of alimony and current divorce laws. Ending alimony will incentivize more men to get married.\r\n2) Ban non citizens from buying homes: The housing crisis is caused by foreign private equity groups and H1-B faggots buying all the homes. This has caused home prices to skyrocket making it impossible for new couples to buy homes.\r\n3) Offer tax breaks: Families who have four or more children and are not on welfare will be exempt from personal income taxes.\r\n4) Impose an immigration moratorium: Immigration is the leading cause of stagnant wages and inflation. A 20 year immigration moratorium will slow down inflation and cause wages to go up. Many young people aren't starting families because they simply can't afford it.", "author": "China4Biden", "created": 1775340352170, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DeplorableNeandertal", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "COMBATTING DECLINING BIRTH RATES: Instead of increasing H1-B / other Visas, we need to encourage more young people to marry / start families by 1) Ending Alimony 2) Ban non citizens from buying homes 3) Offer tax breaks 4) Impose an immigration moratorium", "last_comment_created": 1775361595296, "content": "<ol>\n<li>Ending Alimony: Most men refuse to get married because of alimony and current divorce laws. Ending alimony will incentivize more men to get married.</li>\n<li>Ban non citizens from buying homes: The housing crisis is caused by foreign private equity groups and H1-B faggots buying all the homes. This has caused home prices to skyrocket making it impossible for new couples to buy homes.</li>\n<li>Offer tax breaks: Families who have four or more children and are not on welfare will be exempt from personal income taxes.</li>\n<li>Impose an immigration moratorium: Immigration is the leading cause of stagnant wages and inflation. A 20 year immigration moratorium will slow down inflation and cause wages to go up. Many young people aren't starting families because they simply can't afford it.</li>\n</ol>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 16, "score_up": 146, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZD2QDEn", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 104, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8536599, "raw_content": "", "author": "flp999", "created": 1775346840481, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "CANATIVE", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "rumble.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZD2QDEn.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://rumble.com/v782jfu-nearly-10-of-us-births-are-anchor-babies.html?mref=1wxk5&mc=ehuil", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions